        "subject": "LU-1823 kernel: enable kernel debug options",
        "message": "LU-1823 kernel: enable kernel debug options\n\nThis patch enables the following debug options:\nCONFIG_DEBUG_SPINLOCK\nCONFIG_DEBUG_LOCK_ALLOC\nCONFIG_DEBUG_LOCKDEP\nCONFIG_PROVE_LOCKING\nCONFIG_DEBUG_SPINLOCK_SLEEP\nCONFIG_DEBUG_STACK_USAGE\n\nTest-Parameters: envdefinitions=SLOW=yes testgroup=full\nSigned-off-by: Yu Jian <yujian@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: Ie5e2462d7f6a6d5bf2490d9ff8a8b78d68e0bfd8\n"
